Displace cement with 6.36 m3 of 1.03 SG Retarded Brine (715 lpm), 9.37 m3 of 0.79 SG base oil (715 lpm reducing to 635 lpm) and 0.64 m4 of 1.03 SG Retarded Brine (477 lpm).
